    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for its next adventure? I\u2019m selling my car, and it\u2019s honestly been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in solid shape, runs super smoothly, and has been really well-cared for over the years. It's been perfect for my daily commutes and the occasional weekend getaway! I'm looking for a smooth and easy sale, so feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come take a look. I'd love to see it go to a great new home!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
