      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sorted driver\u2019s car featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, renowned for its 8,000 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies. The high-pressure double-VANOS system functions perfectly, providing a linear torque curve across the rev range. Crucially, the rear subframe has been reinforced with plates to address floor-pan fatigue, and the rod bearings have been replaced\u2014essential preventative maintenance for this high-revving powerplant. Power is sent through a 6-speed manual transmission to a factory limited-slip differential, maintaining excellent mechanical grip. The suspension retains its original geometry with refreshed bushings, ensuring the communicative steering feel and 50/50 weight distribution this chassis is famous for. While it shows honest aesthetic wear, the drivetrain and structural integrity are robust.",
      "price": 32400.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used vehicle. Good condition. Well-maintained. Clean title. Ready for immediate pickup.",
      "price": 31500.0,
