      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a prime example of pride of ownership, offering a perfect balance of performance and reliability. The exterior paint retains a brilliant luster, with only a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small, professionally touched-up scratch on the passenger door that are only visible upon close inspection. The alloy wheels are curb-rash free and wrapped in premium tires with plenty of life left. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the upholstery is free of tears or stains, the dashboard is crack-free, and it has never been smoked in. All power features, including the sunroof, heated seats, and infotainment system, operate exactly as they should. Under the hood, the engine is dry and runs quietly, backed by a comprehensive service log. We recently performed a 60,000-mile service including a fluid flush and new ceramic brake pads. It drives straight, brakes firmly, and offers a smooth, confident ride. This is a dependable, high-quality vehicle that needs nothing but a new garage.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this distinguished vehicle, an exemplary model of sustained mechanical integrity and aesthetic appeal. Meticulously maintained throughout its tenure, this automobile offers a refined driving experience characterized by reliable performance and a well-preserved interior. It serves as an ideal acquisition for the professional seeking a sophisticated balance of utility and prestige. This vehicle has undergone a comprehensive inspection to ensure it meets our rigorous standards for quality and roadworthiness.",
