    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape, runs like a dream, and has clearly been well-cared for over the years. It's perfect for someone looking for a reliable, comfy car that\u2019s ready to hit the road today. I\u2019d love for it to go to a great new home\u2014come take a look and see for yourself!",
      "price": 32500.0,
