      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sorted example of BMW\u2019s high-revving masterpiece. Under the hood, the S54 3.2L inline-six features individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing, delivering a crisp throttle response up to the 8,000 RPM redline. Power is managed by a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and transferred through a limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance is addressed: rod bearings have been replaced, the VANOS system has been overhauled, and the rear subframe has been reinforced with plates. Suspension geometry is maintained via fresh bushings and Bilstein dampers. While the finish shows minor road wear consistent with a well-loved driver, the powertrain and chassis integrity are exceptional.",
